WEBVTT

00:03:26.027 --> 00:03:31.852
I recruited a very able economist
from the World Bank

00:03:31.876 --> 00:03:35.142
to be our minister of finance,

00:03:35.166 --> 00:03:37.937
to lead our debt-relief effort.

00:03:39.410 --> 00:03:44.444
Another to be the minister
of foreign affairs,

00:03:44.468 --> 00:03:51.052
to reactivate our bilateral
and multilateral relationships.

00:03:52.463 --> 00:03:55.423
The first woman chief of police

00:03:57.050 --> 00:04:00.910
to address the fears of our women,